{"tid":2380004,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"html onclick問題","createTime":"2021-01-25T14:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T05:07:25.000Z","uid":78226,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"75f05127d6eca5eb8eb1387cc01c053a25af0372","tid":2380004,"uid":78226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"自己寫緊個網頁諗住自用，Android同Pc正常用到，但發現iphone 同ipad禁個button 都冇反應。個button 用onclick=&ldquo;&rdquo; 上網查左好多篇野都唔知點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇高手知咩事?"},{"pid":"b988fef49d5d86c761a702c545c977458fd2f2a5","tid":2380004,"uid":23094,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:47:08.000Z","msg":"唔好用Global function同onclick attribute<br />\n用 <code>click</code> event handler<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">&lt;button id=&quot;my-button&quot;&gt;My Button&lt;/button&gt;</code></pre><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">const myButton = document.querySelector('#my-button');\nmyButton.addEventListener('click', (event) =&gt; {\n  // do something\n});</code></pre>"},{"pid":"e0689fd47689e5fcc2c1cacaf687d622d3602b68","tid":2380004,"uid":387826,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T17:14:53.000Z","msg":"你去stackoverflow開po問好啲woo"},{"pid":"80758e462df941dc0738f5abb5b12bb230c7298d","tid":2380004,"uid":336298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T18:34:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/1769374/onclick-event-in-select-html-not-working-in-safari\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstackoverflow.com%2Fquestions%2F1769374%2Fonclick-event-in-select-html-not-working-in-safari&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=9b61c5b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/1769374/onclick-event-in-select-html-not-working-in-safari</a>"},{"pid":"b5894cc9ca3fd04f4eeece9051141e6bdd658b1f","tid":2380004,"uid":5159,"like":3,"dislik